Authentication vs Authorization
________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

RBAC is Kubernetes' authorization system. " It is an kubernetes resource which will be responcibl for managig the autorization and autentication and decides who are havibg the ccess to cluster and what are the permission they are allowd to do"


For example:

	Can Vinay create Pods?
	Can Jenkins deploy applications?
	Can Prometheus read metrics?
	Can a developer delete Namespaces?

		RBAC decides who can do what.

Authentication vs Authorization

This is one of the most common interview questions.

Authentication
_______________________
Authentication answers:

Who are you?

Examples:

IAM User
IAM Role
ServiceAccount
Certificate
OIDC
Authorization

Authorization answers:
_____________________
What are you allowed to do?

Examples:

Can create Pods?
Can list Deployments?
Can delete Secrets?



	"RBAC handles authorization".
